Adding Project Title and Slicer 10

Steps

Adding Project Logo

  1.         Click on Insert from ribbon.
  2.         Then click on Image in Elements
  3.         Select the Image from the Extracted file
  4.         General:  X - Position = 0, Y - Position = 0, Width = 152 and Height = 79
  5.          Scaling: Normal

Steps

Adding Colaberry Logo

  1.         Click on Insert from ribbon.
  2.         Then click on Image in Elements
  3.         Select the Image from the Extracted file
  4.         General:  X - Position = 1105, Y - Position = 0, Width = 174 and Height = 78
  5.          Scaling: Normal

Steps

Adding Project Title  and Logo

  1.         Click on the Text box from Home ribbon.
  2.         Begin typing the name of the project (Traffic Violation in USA 2012 - 2016)
  3.         Select the text then change the font size to 28 and and font type to Arial Black
  4.         select the text then font color to #252423 and and make Bold
  5.         General:  X - Position = 160, Y - Position = 0, Width = 1017 and Height = 85




Steps

Adding Date Slicer

  1.     Open Visualization pane 
  2.     Select Slicer visual
  3.     Drag the visual on the dashboard
  4.     Click on Date table and drag Year column from the Date Hierarchy  then place it inside the field
  5.     General : X - Position = 0, Y - Position = 85, Width = 205 and Height = 107
  6.     Slider Header = Off
  7.      Title : On -   Font Color : #FFFFFF, Background Color : #073501, Font Size : 14 and  Font Type : DIN

                            

Steps

Adding Vehicle Type Slicer

  1.     Open Visualization pane 
  2.     Select Slicer visual
  3.     Drag the visual on the dashboard
  4.     Click Vehicle Type  field and place it inside the field
  5.     General : X - Position = 0, Y - Position = 198, Width = 205 and Height = 97
  6.     Slider Header = Off
  7.      Title : On -   Font Color : #FFFFFF, Background Color : #073501, Font Size : 14 and  Font Type : DIN
